TITLE: Implementing IMethodCallParser for Custom Linq Parsing in C#
DESCRIPTION: This C# code snippet demonstrates the implementation of the `IMethodCallParser` interface for custom Linq parsing. It includes methods for matching method call expressions and parsing them into Postgresql "where" clauses, using the example of parsing a custom `IsBlue()` method call on a `ColorTarget` object.
