DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates various methods of the IDocumentCleaner service for removing persisted document state and tearing down document storage.  The examples include completely removing schema objects, deleting all documents and event data, and deleting documents by type or excluding specific types. Requires an IDocumentStore instance.
