TITLE: Configuring Marten with Static Multi-Tenant Databases (C#)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to configure Marten to use a separate database for each tenant using a static mapping of tenant IDs to database connection strings. It uses the `MultiTenantedDatabases()` method to specify the database connection strings for different tenants, and also registers document types and applies all database changes on startup. This requires prior creation of tenant databases.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jasperfx/marten/blob/master/docs/configuration/multitenancy.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: C#
