TITLE: Custom Schema Function in Marten (C#)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to create a custom Postgresql function using `Weasel.Postgresql.Functions.Function` and add it to Marten's extended schema objects. It defines a function named 'iif' that acts as a ternary operator and applies the configuration changes to the database.
