TITLE: Implementing IDocumentSessionListener in Marten (C#)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to implement the `IDocumentSessionListener` interface in Marten to listen for and intercept document persistence events.  This allows for modification of the `IDocumentSession` and its related unit of work before persisting data to the database. The interface includes methods for actions before and after commits, and on document inserts, updates, and deletions.
