TITLE: Subscription Filters
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to filter events for a Marten subscription. It covers including archived events, filtering based on stream type (Invoice), and including specific event types (InvoiceCreated, InvoiceApproved). It registers the subscription with `AddSubscriptionWithServices` and configures the daemon in HotCold mode.
