TITLE: Querying with Select() for deep properties in Marten (C#)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to project deep, nested properties. Specifically, it retrieves `Inner.Number` from the `Target` document where `Number` matches a certain value, and then asserts that the retrieved values are as expected. Requires `theStore` to be an initialized `IDocumentStore` with bulk inserted `Target` documents.
