TITLE: Defining IProjection Interface in Marten (C#)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines the `IProjection` interface in Marten, which serves as the base interface for all event projections. It declares methods for applying projections during both synchronous and asynchronous operations, utilizing `IDocumentOperations` and `StreamAction`.
