TITLE: Custom Serializer Contract (C#)
DESCRIPTION: Customizes the default behavior of the Json.NET serializer to support private property setters during deserialization, which is required for hydrating immutable projections.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jasperfx/marten/blob/master/documentation/documentation/scenarios/immutable_projections_readmodel.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
public class SerializerContract : SerializerFactory
{
    public override JsonContract CreateContract(Type objectType)
    {
        var contract = base.CreateContract(objectType);
        contract.DefaultCreator = () => Activator.CreateInstance(objectType, true);
        contract.IsReference = false;
        foreach (var property in contract.Properties)
        {
            property.Readable = true;
            property.Writable = true;
            property.HasMemberAttribute = true;
        }
        return contract;
    }
}
```

