TITLE: Remove Primitive Element from Collection in Marten (C#)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates removing a primitive element from a child collection using `Patch.Remove()`. The example generates a target object with a number array, selects a random number from the array, and then removes it using the patching API. The result is verified by loading the modified document. Dependencies: Marten, Xunit, Shouldly.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jasperfx/marten/blob/master/docs/documents/partial-updates-patching.md#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
