TITLE: Selecting Single Value with Marten Linq in C#
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to select a single value from a Marten database using Linq. Includes examples of using `Single()`, `SingleOrDefault()`, `First()`, `FirstOrDefault()`, `Last()`, and `LastOrDefault()` methods.  It uses `IDocumentSession` to query the `Target` document type based on specified conditions.
