TITLE: SaveChangesAsync() Sequence Diagram
DESCRIPTION: This Mermaid sequence diagram illustrates the flow of execution when calling `SaveChangesAsync()` on a `DocumentSessionBase`. It shows the interactions between the `Client`, `DocumentSessionBase`, `IUnitOfWork`, `IManagedConnection`, `IDocumentSessionListener`, and `UpdateBatch`, including transaction management, operation sorting, listener invocation, and batched database command execution. Note that event appending workflow is omitted.
