TITLE: ISerializer Interface Definition
DESCRIPTION: Defines the ISerializer interface, which acts as an adapter for JSON serialization within Marten. This interface allows for different JSON serialization libraries or custom configurations to be plugged into the DocumentStore. Implementing this interface enables users to customize how Marten serializes and deserializes documents to/from JSON.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jasperfx/marten/blob/master/documentation/documentation/documents/json/index.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
public interface ISerializer
{
    string ToJson(object document);
    T FromJson<T>(string json);

    // The actual Newtonsoft.Json.JsonSerializer used internally
    JsonSerializer Serializer { get; }

    // Customize the LINQ expression generation
    IExpressionCompiler ExpressionCompiler { get; }

    // Customize the data type mappings to Postgresql
    ITypeNameSource TypeNameSource { get; }

    // Write out JSON to a stream
    void ToJson(object document, Stream stream);

    // Read JSON from a stream
    object FromJson(Type type, Stream stream);
}
```

