TITLE: Jil Serializer Implementation in C#
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to implement the `ISerializer` interface to use the Jil library for JSON serialization in Marten. It handles both serialization and deserialization using Jil's `JSON.Serialize` and `JSON.Deserialize` methods. This custom serializer needs to be registered with the `DocumentStore` to be used by Marten.
